Before doing any project in the Backend - 
Create 2 folders - > frontend and Backend 
In frontEnd > create --.gitignore and .READme file 

in Backend folder - 
>>npm init -y
will add the package.json file (in this below description - key - type , value "module")

>>npm i express nodemon (creates the package-lock.json file and starts the express framework)
"mian": "index.js" 
"scripts":
  "starts":"node index.js"
  "dev";"nodemon index.js"


Under node modules - 
create index.js file   (main file for the backend logic ,, where the all the framework, DB are initiated and api are called )
